divs: sighting detailssighting report: this incident occurred approx. 2:00am. mid 1995. it was a very clear beautiful night. i was fishing on a boat with a friend of mine, nate. it was getting late and we decided to call it a night , as we approached the boat dock we noticed a glowing amber colored light\object hovering over an overpass next to the dock. we were approx 15092 from the overpass and the object was approx 40=92 above the overpass. this light\object bobbed up and down and side to side as if it was floating on an invisible ocean. we looked at each other and said =93what the hell is that=94. i immediately stopped the boat and we watched it for a few seconds =96 it then instantly shoot upwards =96 it appeared to have gone to the edge of the atmosphere. it moved so fast that it left =93trails=94 from the point it was at to the point above us where it stopped. at this time it appeared as a very bright amber colored star. as we continued to watch it for a few seconds we noticed a red ring of light start to appear\pulsate around it. the red =93ring=94 first started out dim and as it pulsated it got brighter. at the point of it=92s brightest moment the amber object =93disappeared=94 into the ring. as soon as the object went =93into=94 the ring the ring shrunk and faded away. the amber light looked slightly =93fuzzy=94 as if it was dissipating heat from it =96 like the ripple affect you see from a hot road or hot car hood on a hot summer day. it did look like an object radiating light rather than just a light in the sky. it appeared to have =93substance=94 to it. we did not hear any noise coming from the object.
